Defaults to men if just given the trigger words. For some reason this lora doesn't mix with other lora/ti it's trained the same as my others so I'm not sure what's up, hopefully I can fix that in later versions. Does still work with selective lora like fashion girl (credits zakp), which just shows I still have a lot to learn.
